                "component": "Text",
                "content": "# Body surcharge"
              },
              {
                "component": "Text",
                "content": "Our bodies are equipped with a super-efficient defense system: stress. When we experience something that is threatening, the brain quickly switches to focusing on escaping or fighting."
              }
            ]
          },
          {
            "component": "ButtonGroup",
            "content": [
